    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> grated ginger</strong> and <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>pak choi</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until the pak choi starts to soften</p>",
