    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>peanut butter</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1] </span><strong>lime</strong> and 100ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [150ml]</span> <strong>water</strong> to the pak choi and<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 1 min, or until the liquid is well mixed and starts to thicken slightly – this is your <strong>pak choi & peanut sauce</strong></p>",
