      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy tofu</strong> and <strong>pak choi & peanut sauce</strong> over the<strong> wholewheat noodles</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> chopped coriander</strong>, <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion </strong>and<strong> chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
